long_description: i'm thrilled you found my site and are exploring the images i've created. let me tell you a bit about myself so you can get to know the person behind the lens. i'm jeff wales, and i've been a photographer for the past fifteen years. my journey was began with taking photographs while traveling the world rock climbing and bouldering. i thrive on capturing the beauty and authenticity of those "in-between moments" that often go unnoticed. naturally nomadic, i am fascinated by meeting new people, visiting new places, and creating new life experiences. at jeff wales photography, i am dedicated to capturing the essence of your special moments through natural, timeless images. with extensive experience in family and wedding photography, i effortlessly connect with clients, making them feel relaxed, comfortable, and truly seen. each photography session is customized and tailored to create a unique, personalized experience that reflects your individual style and taste. let's create something beautiful together.
business_tags: portraits & weddings | weddings photography | wedding photographs | family and portraits | photography session
